steps.name: Login with username and password
Enter username
Enter password
Click login button
Click on account menu item
Get the first account ID
Click on the account to view details
Get available balance from account details
Click on transfer menu item
Enter transfer details
Select source account
Enter recipient account number
Enter amount
Enter payment content
Get available balance
Get transfer amount from transfer details form
Get transfer message from transfer details form
Get recipient account ID from transfer details form
Get recipient account name from transfer details form
Click on Confirm button to open transaction confirm form
Get source account ID from transfer confirmation form
Get transfer amount from transfer confirmation form
Get transfer message from transfer confirmation form
Get recipient account ID from transfer confirmation form
Get recipient name from transfer confirmation form
Get receive OTP via email text from transfer confirmation form
Click on confirm button to open OTP entry form
